&lt;p&gt;Suppose we have Workspace 1 with one Left Terminal and another V-Split Container [Top Terminal + Bottom Terminal]. So, how to move the bottom terminal (inside the V-split Container) to the left, splitting vertically the left terminal?&lt;/p&gt;

